<item>
 <title>Salvatore Vicari</title>
 <link>https://www.davisfellowsforpeace.org/fellows/2021-fellows/arabic/node/2050</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-project-year field-type-number-integer field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Year of Fellowship:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;2021&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-language-school field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;School:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Arabic&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-area-of-interest field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Area of Interest:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;—&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Salvatore Vicari &lt;/span&gt;is Médecins Sans Frontières (Doctors Without Borders) humanitarian affairs advisor in the Middle East. In his role, he conducts research and coordinates advocacy initiatives in crises across the region. His work covers issues such as access to humanitarian assistance and protection of the medical mission in conflicts.&lt;/p&gt;
