<item>
 <title>Sophia Schroeder</title>
 <link>https://www.davisfellowsforpeace.org/fellows/2021-fellows/arabic/node/2044</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-project-year field-type-number-integer field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Year of Fellowship:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;2021&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-language-school field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;School:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Arabic&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-area-of-interest field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Area of Interest:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;—&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Sophia Schroeder &lt;/span&gt;is a PhD student at UCL in London, focusing on the role of domestic courts in consociational systems of power-sharing, such as in Lebanon and Northern Ireland. She seeks to understand how courts contribute to conflict management and resolution in deeply divided societies, in particular in post-conflict societies.&lt;/p&gt;
