 <link>https://www.davisfellowsforpeace.org/fellows/2021-fellows/arabic/node/2038</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-project-year field-type-number-integer field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Year of Fellowship:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;2021&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-language-school field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;School:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Arabic&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-area-of-interest field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Area of Interest:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;—&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Lucy Provan &lt;/span&gt;is a London-based journalist and producer/director. Her work focuses on the Middle East, gender, and democracy. She is a One World Media and International Women’s Media Fund grantee. Lucy works in print and documentary. She has lived and worked in France, Tunisia, Egypt, Libya, the Occupied Palestinian Territories, Sudan, and Jordan.&lt;/p&gt;
