 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-project-year field-type-number-integer field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Year of Fellowship:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;2021&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-language-school field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;School:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;Arabic&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-area-of-interest field-type-text field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Area of Interest:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;—&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Joshua Levkowitz &lt;/span&gt;is interested in conflict and culture in the Middle East. He lived and worked on social cohesion and participatory governance in northern Iraq. He recently moved to Istanbul to research and write on Syrian migration and placemaking in Syria’s neighboring countries.&lt;/p&gt;
